ActionMailerTls
===============

Use GMail SMTP server to send emails in Rails ActionMailer

Example
=======

Place code snippet in config/environment.rb

ActionMailer::Base.server_settings = {
  :address => "smtp.gmail.com",
  :port => 587,
  :domain => "mycompany.com",
  :authentication => :plain,
  :user_name => "username",
  :password => "password"
}

